{"lemma":"قَدْرُ","slug":"قَدْرُ","root":"ق.د.ر","root_slug":"ق-د-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-د-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"قَدْر","root":"قدر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":23},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35273","n35278","n35279","n35280","n35281"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have power"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be equal to, to be up to"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be able to","examples":[{"text":"كي نضمِّن أن توصلنا قراراتنا في المجالات الأخلاقية إلى نتائج جيدة، لا نقدر أن نتَّكل فقط على إحساسنا أو رأي الآخرين.","english":"In order to ensure that our decisions in ethical areas lead to good results, we cannot rely solely on our own feelings or the opinions of others."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to determine, to fix"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to estimate, to assess, to forecast"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to foresee, to wager"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to enable someone to something (with accusative and عَلَى)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"quantity, quantum, measure, magnitude, size, bulk, proportion, extent, space, amount, sum, number","examples":[{"text":"هٰذَا قَدْرُ ذَاكَ","english":"this is as much as that"},{"text":"هُمْ قَدْرُ مِئَةٍ","english":"they are as many as 100"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"worth, value"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"greatness, majesty, honorableness, nobleness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"preordained destiny, predestination, fate"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"will of God, divine decree, providence"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"might, power, position, influence, wealth"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of قَدِرَ (qadira, “to be able to”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fate, destiny"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"power, capacity, faculty"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ability"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"competence"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sufficiency, riches"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"quantity, measure, size, space, amount, sum, number"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"worth, value"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"greatness, majesty, honorableness, nobleness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pot, kettle, cooking pot","examples":[{"text":"قِدْر نُحَاس","english":"copper pot"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"*Compare Hebrew קְדֵרָה (q'derá)"},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35273","headword_ar":"قدّر","root":"qdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqodiyrN","text_ar":"تَقْدِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, in most of its senses. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He meditated, considered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exercised thought in arranging and preparing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing or an affair; (T, K, * El-Basáïr;) either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making use of his reason, and building thereon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the doing of which is praiseworthy; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"according to his desire or appetite;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the Kur, lxxiv. 18 and 19; the doing of which is blameable; (ElBasáïr;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of marks, whereby to cut it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He intended"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing or an affair;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he determined upon it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) [Said of God,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He decreed, appointed, ordained, destined, predestined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"predetermined"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing.] ―         -b4-  [Hence, app.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qd~r ka*aA","text_ar":"قدّر كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in grammar,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He meant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"held,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made, such a thing to be supplied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understood."},{"kind":"text","text":"You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqodiyruhu ka*aA","text_ar":"تَقْدِيرُهُ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a phrase's)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"implied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"virtual, meaning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meaning by implication, is thus."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuqad~aru bika*aA","text_ar":"يُقَدَّرُ بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its implied meaning is to be expressed by saying thus."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqodiyrFA","text_ar":"تَقْدِيرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said in the sense of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"implicatively,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"virtually,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafoZFA","text_ar":"لَفْظًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"or literally. ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He supposed such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEala","text_ar":"جَعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaEa","text_ar":"صَنَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". Ex., in the Kur, [xli. 9,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqad~ara","text_ar":"وَقَدَّرَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhaA A^aqowaAtahaA","text_ar":"فِيهَا اَقْوَاتَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And He made therein its foods,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aliments."},{"kind":"text","text":"And it is said in the Kur, [x. 5,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqad~arahu manaAzila","text_ar":"وَقَدَّرَهُ مَنَازِلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And hath made for it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the moon]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mansions."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He knew."},{"kind":"text","text":"So in the Kur, xv. 60; and lxxiii. 20, according to the Basáïr. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qd~rhu","text_ar":"قدّرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqodiyrN","text_ar":"تَقْدِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He asserted him to be,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"named him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"called him, a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadariY~","text_ar":"قَدَرِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Fr, Sgh, K:) but this is post-classical. (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qd~rhu","text_ar":"قدّرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aqdrhu","text_ar":"اقدرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [the latter of which is the more common,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He empowered him; enabled him; rendered him able."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aqdrhu A@ll~`hu EalaY ka*aA","text_ar":"اقدرهُ ا@للّٰهُ عَلَى كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God empowered him, enabled him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered him able, to do such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Fr","Sgh","K","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n35278","headword_ar":"قَدْرٌ","root":"qdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity, quantum, measure, magnitude, size, bulk, proportion, extent, space, amount, sum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"number attained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; (S, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qudorN","text_ar":"قُدْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Sgh, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqodaArN","text_ar":"مِقْدَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA qadoru h`*aA","text_ar":"هٰذَا قَدْرُ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadaruhu","text_ar":"قَدَرُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is the like of this"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in quantity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is commensurate with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proportionate to, this;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h*A","text_ar":"هذا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h*A bimiqodaAri","text_ar":"هذا بِمِقْدَارِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo qadoru","text_ar":"هُمْ قَدْرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miAy^pK","text_ar":"مِايةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mAy^p","text_ar":"ماية"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadaru","text_ar":"قَدَرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are as many as a hundred."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a biqadori Haq~ihi","text_ar":"اَخَذَ بِقَدْرِ حَقِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biqadarihi","text_ar":"بِقَدَرِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bimiqodaArihi","text_ar":"بِمِقْدَارِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took as much as his due,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"right."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraA^a biqadori AlfaAtiHapi","text_ar":"قَرَاَ بِقَدْرِ الفَاتِحَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biqadarihaA","text_ar":"بِقَدَرِهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bimiqodaArihaA","text_ar":"بِمِقْدَارِهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He read as much as the Fátihah."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqamotu Einodahu qadora A^ano yafoEala ka*aA","text_ar":"اَقَمْتُ عِنْدَهُ قَدْرَ اَنْ يَفْعَلَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I remained at his abode long enough for him to do thus."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Meyd, TA.) But you say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a EalaY qadarK","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ عَلَى قَدَرٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", thus only, with fet-h [to the dál, as is shown by what precedes in the Msb,] as meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It came according to measure;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was conformable; it matched; it suited."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAwaza qadorahu","text_ar":"جَاوَزَ قَدْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarahu","text_ar":"قَدَرَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He overstepped, transgressed, went beyond,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exceeded, his proper measure, bound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the same is said of a thing]. (L, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"End","text_ar":"عند"},{"kind":"text","text":"; &c.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasa baEiydu Alqadori","text_ar":"فَرَسَ بَعِيدُ القَدْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse that takes long,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wide, steps."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA qadoriY","text_ar":"هٰذَا قَدْرِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is sufficient for me."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-  [Hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Estimation, value, worth, account, rank, quality,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"degree of dignity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greatness, majesty, honourableness, nobleness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, * TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gravity of character;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lahu EinodiY qadorN","text_ar":"مَا لَهُ عِنْدِى قَدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has no honourableness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gravity of character, in my opinion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) In the words of the Kur, [vi. 91,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamaA qadaruwA A@ll~`ha Haq~a qadorihi","text_ar":"وَمَا قَدَرُوا ا@للّٰهَ حَقَّ قَدْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [for explanations of which see 1,] we may also correctly read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarihi","text_ar":"قَدَرِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadorN","text_ar":"قَدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) [the latter of which is the more common,] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Msb, K) alone, (Msb,) or both, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqodaArN","text_ar":"مِقْدَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqodiyrN","text_ar":"تَقْدِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqodarap","text_ar":"مَقْدَرَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h only [to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"d","text_ar":"د"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Decree, appointment, ordinance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"destiny:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is decreed, appointed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaA='N","text_ar":"قَضَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HukomN","text_ar":"حُكْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adapted"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to a particular case"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Lth, JK, Az, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by God;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;) expl. by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaA='N muwaf~aqN","text_ar":"قَضَا=ءٌ مُوَفَّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, JK, &c.,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yuqad~iruhu A@ll~`hu mina AlqaDaA='i","text_ar":"مَا يُقَدِّرُهُ ا@للّٰهُ مِنَ القَضَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaDaA='u Al~a*iY","text_ar":"القَضَا=ءُ الَّذِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuqad~iruhu A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"يُقَدِّرُهُ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) [accord. to general usage, it differs from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaA='N","text_ar":"قَضَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; this latter signifying a general decree of God, as that every living being shall die; whereas ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a particular decree of God,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as that a certain man shall die at a particular time and place &c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"particular predestination:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaDaA='u waAlqadaru","text_ar":"القَضَا=ءُ وَالقَدَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the general and particular decrees of God;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"general and particular predestination"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fate and destiny."},{"kind":"text","text":"The term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is variously explained by different schools and sects: but its proper meaning seems to be that given above on the authority of Lth.] The pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqodaArN","text_ar":"اَقْدَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) and of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqaAdiyru miqodaArN","text_ar":"مَقَادِيرُ مِقْدَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^umuwru tajoriY","text_ar":"الاُمُورُ تَجْرِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biqadari A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"بِقَدَرِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bimiqodaArihi","text_ar":"بِمِقْدَارِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Events have their course by the decree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of God."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapu Alqadori","text_ar":"لَيْلَةُ القَدْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night of decree,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2496},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (TA. See also 1.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadorN","text_ar":"قَدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L) A camel's or horse's saddle"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of middling size;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L, K;) and in like manner ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAdirN","text_ar":"قَادِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a horse's saddle,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between small and large;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or this last signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy, that does not wound;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAtirN","text_ar":"قَاتِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqotadarN","text_ar":"مُقْتَدَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqotadirN","text_ar":"مُقْتَدِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, but see 8,) a thing, (JK,) or anything, (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of middling size,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether in length or tallness or in width or breadth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mqtdru","text_ar":"مقتدرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxaloqi","text_ar":"الخَلْقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying a man, and a mountain-goat, and an antelope,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of middling make:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mqtdru AlTuwli","text_ar":"مقتدرُ الطُولِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of middling stature"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tallness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qudaArN","text_ar":"قُدَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^u*unN qadoraA='u","text_ar":"اُذُنٌ قَدْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An ear neither small nor large."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K.)       -A4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qudorapN","text_ar":"قُدْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","Fr","Sgh","S","JK","TA","M","Lth","Az","A","L","T"]},{"entry_id":"n35279","headword_ar":"قُدْرٌ","root":"qdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadorN","text_ar":"قَدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n35280","headword_ar":"قِدْرٌ","root":"qdr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cooking-pot; a vessel in which one cooks:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [and it very often means the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"food contained therein;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pottage"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any kind: (see, for an ex., 3 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"glw","text_ar":"غلو"},{"kind":"text","text":":)] of the fem. gender (Msb, K, TA) without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or it is made fem. (S, K) as well as masc., accord. to some: but he who asserts it to be made masc. is led into error by a saying of Th: AM observes, as to the saying of the Arabs, related by Th,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA raA^ayotu qidorFA","text_ar":"مَا رَاَيْتُ قِدْرًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galaY A^asoraEa minohaA","text_ar":"غَلَى اَسْرَعَ مِنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not seen a cooking-pot that has boiled quicker than it"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qdr","text_ar":"قدر"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not here meant to be made masc. but the meaning is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA rA^yt $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"ما رايت شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"glY","text_ar":"غلى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not seen a thing that has boiled"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and similar to this is the saying in the Kur, [xxxiii. 52,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yaHil~u laka Aln~isaA='u","text_ar":"لَا يَحِلُّ لَكَ النِّسَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA yHl~","text_ar":"لا يحلّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lk $aYo'N mina Aln~isaA='i","text_ar":"لك شَىْءٌ مِنَ النِّسَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the dim. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qudayorN","text_ar":"قُدَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", contr. to analogy; (S, TA;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qudayorapN","text_ar":"قُدَيْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", because"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qidorN","text_ar":"قِدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is fem.; (Msb;) or both: (TA:) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quduwrN","text_ar":"قُدُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, K:) it has no other pl. (TA.) [See a tropical ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HAmK","text_ar":"حامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","TA","S"]},{"entry_id":"n35281","headword_ar":"قَدَرٌ","root":"qdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadorN","text_ar":"قَدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", throughout: (where its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqodaArN","text_ar":"اَقْدَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; K, * TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qudorapN","text_ar":"قُدْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (in which sense also its pl. is as above; K.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaborN","text_ar":"جَبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqodaArN","text_ar":"مِقْدَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place, of promise; an appointed time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoEidN","text_ar":"مَوْعِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See Kur, xx. 42.]"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}